The Image widget in Flutter is used to display pictures or graphics in your app тАФ like logos, backgrounds, product photos, etc.
You can load images from different sources тАФ assets, network (URL), files, or memory.

project_name/
 тФЬтФА lib/
 тФЬтФА assets/
 тФВ   тФФтФА images/
 тФВ       тФФтФА myimage.png
 тФФтФА pubspec.yaml

ЁЯз▒ Step 2: Update pubspec.yaml  uncameent 
flutter:
  assets:
    - assets/images/


